About the War between the Greatland Kingdom and
the Demons by magical historian Arnaldo Croix.
Reading a book
Not reading

The Greatland Kingdom is an island nation located
in the state of Yula. It is known as the most
advanced in magical research and also has the
highest number of demon appearances.

The first magician, Enhed. Solomon, is also from
the Greatland Kingdom.

The war with the demons has been ongoing since the
year 800 in the Divine Calendar, and of course,
the first believers were also from the Greatland
Kingdom.

Those who fight using the divine tools received
from the gods are called heroes, and those who
fight using magic are called magicians. Sisters
are able to perform miracles through their strong
faith.

A thousand years have passed since the start of
the war, but there is still no sign of it ending.
The First Magician Magical Historian Analdo Croche
Reading a book
Not reading

The beginning of magic dates back to the year 900
in the Divine Calendar. It is said that the first
magician, Gnoth Magos, made a contract with a
demon and used magic.

Gnoth Magos belonged to a hero party that defeated
one of the Seven Great Demon Kings, Belial.

Her contributions to the magician community were
tremendous, and she was also involved in the
establishment of the Magic Association.

Many of the oldest magics were created by her, and
she was called a genius. However, because of that,
she was disliked by the Samuel Church.

It is said that in the end, she was captured and
executed, but no one has claimed to have seen her
corpse.
About Magic - Mage Maya Nestra
Reading a book
Don't read it

Magic is a technique used by demons. It is the
ability to manifest mysterious phenomena that
cannot be achieved by human power.

Magic is used by utilizing magical power. Magical
power exists within one's own body, but it also
exists in the atmosphere. The amount of magical
power that exists in the atmosphere is far
greater, and utilizing this is the key to using
powerful magic.

The amount of magical power in the atmosphere is
greater in Hell. Therefore, the closer you get to
underground, the more abundant the amount of
magical power becomes. However, magical power
gives birth to demons.

Human-used magic is mostly learned by analyzing
and acquiring the magic used by demons.

Occasionally, there are those with talent who can
develop new magic, but only a limited few are
capable of doing so.

And most of them are far inferior to the magic
used by demons.

About Caledony Magic Academy by Wizard Gary
Meizers.
Reading a book
Not reading

Caledony Magic Academy is the oldest magic academy
created by its founder and first principal, Enhed.
Solomon.

The academy was secretly created to train wizards
for the battle against demons. However, it was
discovered by the Samuel Church and there were
times when it was temporarily closed.

After that, it became an academy recognized by the
country through persuasion from the Magic
Association.

The Greatland Kingdom, where the academy is
located, is the most prosperous region for magic
in the world, and there are many students who come
to study from other countries.

In addition to the Greatland Kingdom, there are
also the Phylam Magic Girls' Academy and the
Owadour Magic Vocational School, both of which
have become sister schools.
About Demons by Priest Isabelle Madmarie
Reading a book
Not reading

Demons are the enemies of humanity who reside in
the Empire of Hell. The information I am about to
present was obtained from the treacherous demon
Barberito.

The treacherous demon Barberito is a foolish
individual who was captured by the hero Micaelis
and tortured to extract information about the
Empire of Hell.

In the Empire of Hell, there are seven demons who
govern different regions. Among them, the most
powerful is the Gluttonous King Beelzebuth, who
currently serves as the emperor.

The Demon King possesses a power known as the
Demon Lord Authority, which allows them to freely
command demons below the Demon King. They also
possess powerful magic that can only be used by
the Demon King.

Demons have ranks and they are inherited through
generations. It seems that powerful demons can
also rise to power if vacancies arise.

In the year 900 of the Divine Era, a hero defeated
the arrogant King Belial, and it is believed that
the throne has remained vacant ever since.

Demons without intelligence are referred to as
monsters, and monsters indiscriminately attack
humans and demons alike. However, it is said that
if one defeats the leader of a group and
demonstrates their strength, they will no longer
be attacked.
About Unusual Status Ailments by Mage Maya Nestra
Reading a book
Not reading

Here I will show the status ailments that I have
discovered.

OvervoltageHP decreases by 10% each time. When a
monster enters the overvoltage state, it will use
unusual magic.

'Awakening' increases magic power by 1.5 times,
but HP gradually decreases.
'Wound' HP is being reduced.
'Mana Rampage' MP is being depleted.

'Berserker' doubles magic power, but defense
decreases.

'Light Resistance' Light attribute attacks become
almost ineffective.
'Cautious' HP is greatly reduced.
'Abyss State' Magic power greatly increases.

In addition, most lewd status ailments usually
cause a decrease in magic power and maximum MP.
